			<h2><a href="/blog/anthropic-claude-3-opus-bedrock/">AWS launch Anthropic Claude 3 Opus on Amazon Bedrock</a></h2>
			<h3><span title="Seattle, Washington, USA">Seattle</span> | Published <time>16 April 2024</time> in <a href="/categories/ai">AI</a> | 10 minute read | <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=AWS%20launch%20Anthropic%20Claude%203%20Opus%20on%20Amazon%20Bedrock&url=http%3a%2f%2flocalhost%3a1314%2fblog%2fanthropic-claude-3-opus-bedrock%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/twitter-x.svg" alt="Share this post on X" title="Share this post on X" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=http%3a%2f%2flocalhost%3a1314%2fblog%2fanthropic-claude-3-opus-bedrock%2f&xdOrigin=http%3a%2f%2flocalhost%3a1314%2f&xd_origin_host=http%3a%2f%2flocalhost%3a1314%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/linkedin.svg" alt="Share this post on LinkedIn" title="Share this post on LinkedIn" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Have a read&body=http%3a%2f%2flocalhost%3a1314%2fblog%2fanthropic-claude-3-opus-bedrock%2f"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/envelope.svg" alt="Share this post by Email" title="Share this post by Email" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://localhost:1314/blog/anthropic-claude-3-opus-bedrock/" onclick="copyURL('copyit'); return false;" id="copyit"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Copy the Permalink to this post" title="Copy the Permalink to this post" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/anthropics-claude-3-opus-model-on-amazon-bedrock/" target="_blank" title="Read the AWS blog post about this here"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/box-arrow-up-right.svg" alt="Seattle, Washington, USA" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		
		
		<p>This just in! Anthropic&rsquo;s Claude 3 Opus foundation model is now available on Amazon Bedrock, joining Claude Sonnet and Claude Haiku. Bedrock is now the first and only place to offer all three Claude 3 models in general availability.</p>
		
